11#include "pc/transceiver_list.h"
12
13#include "rtc_base/checks.h"
14
15namespace webrtc {
16
17void TransceiverStableState::set_newly_created() {
18 RTC_DCHECK(!has_m_section_);
19 newly_created_ = true;
20}
21
22void TransceiverStableState::SetMSectionIfUnset(
23 absl::optional<std::string> mid,
24 absl::optional<size_t> mline_index) {
25 if (!has_m_section_) {
26 mid_ = mid;
27 mline_index_ = mline_index;
28 has_m_section_ = true;
29 }
30}
31
32void TransceiverStableState::SetRemoteStreamIdsIfUnset(
33 const std::vector<std::string>& ids) {
34 if (!remote_stream_ids_.has_value()) {
35 remote_stream_ids_ = ids;
36 }
37}
38
39void TransceiverStableState::SetInitSendEncodings(
40 const std::vector<RtpEncodingParameters>& encodings) {
41 init_send_encodings_ = encodings;
42}
43
44std::vector<RtpTransceiver*> TransceiverList::ListInternal() const {
45 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&sequence_checker_);
46 std::vector<RtpTransceiver*> internals;
47 for (auto transceiver : transceivers_) {
48 internals.push_back(transceiver->internal());
49 }
50 return internals;
51}
52
53RtpTransceiverProxyRefPtr TransceiverList::FindBySender(
54 rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpSenderInterface> sender) const {
55 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&sequence_checker_);
56 for (auto transceiver : transceivers_) {
57 if (transceiver->sender() == sender) {
58 return transceiver;
59 }
60 }
61 return nullptr;
62}
63
64RtpTransceiverProxyRefPtr TransceiverList::FindByMid(
65 const std::string& mid) const {
66 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&sequence_checker_);
67 for (auto transceiver : transceivers_) {
68 if (transceiver->mid() == mid) {
69 return transceiver;
70 }
71 }
72 return nullptr;
73}
74
75RtpTransceiverProxyRefPtr TransceiverList::FindByMLineIndex(
76 size_t mline_index) const {
77 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(&sequence_checker_);
78 for (auto transceiver : transceivers_) {
79 if (transceiver->internal()->mline_index() == mline_index) {
80 return transceiver;
81 }
82 }
83 return nullptr;
84}
